<L>__{exterior fire escape}
<A>__{they descend the fire escape. they reach the end. the fire escape stays rigid. doc cautiously steps on to the tilted steps. he turns and with the suitcase crosses to the end. throws the bag and the shotgun across the 6 foot gap to the retaining wall, preparing to jump. rudy comes out of the room onto the fire escape holding his .44. he looks down at doc, then slowly raises his gun. carol screams. doc jumps. rudy fires. doc is hit in the side (flesh wound). in the air he spins and lands. rudy fires again and again as he runs down the fire escape. doc rolls, picks up the shotgun and fires. rudy's time has come. the jumbo charges mash him back against the wall and off the fire escape. carol runs almost staggering and gets ready to jump the six feet. the fire escape. begins to sink. carol looks at doc mutely, as she sinks beneath the retaining wall.}
